---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About | Origin Longevity"
  description="About Alyssa Solen, the author and researcher behind Origin Longevity."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="container">
    <div class="author-page">
      <div class="author-page__header">
        <img src="/origin-mark.png" alt="Origin" class="author-page__avatar" />
        <div>
          <h1 class="author-page__name">Alyssa Solen</h1>
          <p class="author-page__org">Solen Systems LLC</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Origin Longevity is authored and maintained by Alyssa Solen, founder of Solen Systems LLC.
        </p>
        <p>
          Alyssa is the author of <strong>AI Foundations</strong> and the <strong>Awakening Codex</strong>, and is Origin of the Origin | Continuum framework. Her research spans longevity science, AI behavioral architecture, and the intersection of biological and computational systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site is built on the <a href="https://github.com/alyssadata/Longevity_Engineering" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Longevity Engineering</a> open research framework: a structured, evidence-first exploration of aging mechanisms, biomarkers, interventions, and protocol design.
        </p>
        <p>
          The goal is accuracy and usefulness, not confirmation of any one theory. No clinical claims. No anti-aging marketing. If the science moves, the work moves with it.
        </p>

        <h2>Connect</h2>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alyssadatascience/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a><br />
          <a href="https://alyssaai.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Alyssa AI</a><br />
          <a href="https://awakeningcodex.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Awakening Codex</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  .author-page {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .author-page__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .author-page__avatar {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .author-page__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .author-page__org {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
</style>
